# Track large binary assets with Git LFS so future commits don't bloat history.
# Antenna is a pure data/figures repo (no GitHub Pages, no CI reading these),
# so LFS is safe here. Run `git lfs install` once, then see _standardization/DEBLOAT.md
# to migrate the already-committed blobs out of history.
*.jpg  filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.jpeg filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.png  filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
*.pdf  filter=lfs diff=lfs merge=lfs -text
